data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_10","content":"../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/brand-spec.md:41:- Editorial serif headlines create the brand feel; practical sans body copy keeps transactional details readable.\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/profitslocal-email-system.html:23:    <div><p>A production-ready HTML email system for Resend: table-based email layouts, CTA-safe URL handling, compact detail tables, and ProfitsLocal’s warm editorial brand translated into customer operations.</p><div class=\"chips\"><span class=\"chip\">No naked URLs</span><span class=\"chip\">Table layout</span><span class=\"chip\">Responsive</span></div></div>\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/profitslocal-email-system.html:37:            <tr><td style=\"padding:20px 28px 24px;border-top:1.5px solid #17191C;background:#FFF6EC\"><p style=\"margin:0;font:13px/20px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#5E6268\">Sent by ProfitsLocal from <strong style=\"color:#17191C\">hi@profitslocal.com</strong>. You’re receiving this because {{customer_business_name}} started a ProfitsLocal project.</p></td></tr>\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/profitslocal-email-system.html:86:    <div class=\"section-title\"><h2>Implementation Handoff</h2><span>Resend template system</span></div>\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/profitslocal-email-system.html:95:      <div class=\"card\"><h3>Resend variables</h3><ul><li>Identity: {{customer_first_name}}, {{customer_business_name}}, {{project_name}}.</li><li>Commerce: {{payment_amount}}, {{receipt_number}}, {{receipt_url}}.</li><li>Actions: {{intake_url}}, {{preview_url}}, {{approve_url}}, {{revision_url}}, {{domain_setup_url}}, {{asset_url}}.</li><li>Status: {{domain_name}}, {{domain_status_label}}, {{next_check_window}}, {{published_domain}}, {{published_at}}, {{asset_name}}.</li></ul></div>\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/index.html:291:        <p class=\"hero-copy\">A production-ready HTML email system for Resend: table-based layouts, CTA-safe URL handling, compact detail tables, and ProfitsLocal’s warm editorial brand translated into customer operations.</p>\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/index.html:372:                        <p style=\"margin:0; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:13px; line-height:20px; color:#5E6268;\">Sent by ProfitsLocal from <strong style=\"color:#17191C;\">hi@profitslocal.com</strong>. You’re receiving this because {{customer_business_name}} started a ProfitsLocal project.</p>\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/index.html:696:        <span>Resend template system</span>\n../da2a113e-bfed-42c4-849c-03035afb170d/index.html:742:          <h3>Resend variables</h3>\n../opa-bar-mezze-restaurant-open-design-1778137259385/contact.html:59:        <p>The original contact form notes general enquiries only; table bookings should go through the bookings page.</p>\n../dd72d0b6-5e99-48e7-a449-1045affbcb98/index.html:1749:            <p>A revision is any requested change to the website: logo, text, content, design taste, contact forms, sections, or adding and removing items.</p>\n../od-handoff-roofer-smoke-open-design-1778271330913/index.html:401:          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">Use the primary call button when the number is supplied. The form is routed for the existing Resend transactional email flow to notify hi@profitslocal.com.</p>\n../od-handoff-roofer-smoke-open-design-1778271330913/index.html:407:          <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"to\" value=\"hi@profitslocal.com\" />\n../od-handoff-roofer-smoke-open-design-1778271330913/index.html:445:      <span class=\"meta\">Brisbane roofing enquiries · routed to hi@profitslocal.com</span>\n../od-handoff-roofer-smoke-open-design-1778271330913/index.html:468:        statusEl.textContent = 'Demo form ready. Connect /api/contact to the existing Resend flow before launch.';\n","isError":false}

