data: {"type":"tool_use","id":"item_13","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"/bin/zsh -lc \"cp ../od-handoff-roofer-smoke-open-design-1778271330913/index.html index.html && perl -0pi -e 's/href=\\\"tel:\\\"/href=\\\"tel:0424371622\\\"/g; s/Call now<\\\\/a>/Call now 0424 371 622<\\\\/a>/g; s/>Call now<\\\\//>Call now 0424 371 622<\\\\//g; s/Phone number intentionally left unset for demo handoff\\\\./Call direct: 0424 371 622. Demo copy only; final service details can be confirmed before launch./; s/Core service/Gutters/; s/A flexible slot for the business to name its highest-value roof restoration offer once the final sales script is confirmed\\\\./Gutter-related enquiry copy for homeowners dealing with overflow, blockage, roofline wear, or maintenance before storm season./; s/Emergency or fast response/Pressure cleaning/g; s/Conversion copy for urgent roofing concerns, focused on quick contact and a clear next step without promising unavailable hours\\\\./Practical pressure cleaning copy for roofs, gutters, and exterior surfaces that need careful preparation before restoration or respray work./; s/Emergency or fast response\\\\n/Pressure cleaning\\\\n/g; s/Use the primary call button when the number is supplied\\\\./Use the primary call button for the fastest enquiry path./; s/What do you need help with\\\\?/Service needed/; s/<option>Emergency or fast response<\\\\/option>/<option>Gutters<\\\\/option>\\\\n              <option>Pressure cleaning<\\\\/option>/; s/<label for=\\\"message\\\">Roof details<\\\\/label>/<label for=\\\"message\\\">Message<\\\\/label>/; s/Suburb, roof concern, and the best time to call back\\\\./Suburb, roof concern, access notes, or photos available./; s/<\\\\/div>\\\\n          <button class=\\\"btn btn-primary\\\" type=\\\"submit\\\">Send enquiry<\\\\/button>/<\\\\/div>\\\\n          <div class=\\\"field\\\">\\\\n            <label for=\\\"preferred-call-time\\\">Preferred call time<\\\\/label>\\\\n            <input class=\\\"input\\\" id=\\\"preferred-call-time\\\" name=\\\"preferred_call_time\\\" autocomplete=\\\"off\\\" placeholder=\\\"e.g. Weekday morning\\\" />\\\\n          <\\\\/div>\\\\n          <button class=\\\"btn btn-primary\\\" type=\\\"submit\\\">Send enquiry<\\\\/button>/; s/<h3>Share the roof concern<\\\\/h3>\\\\n                <p>Restoration, capping, respray, repair, and urgent-response needs are captured in familiar homeowner language\\\\.<\\\\/p>/<h3>Share the roof concern<\\\\/h3>\\\\n                <p>Restoration, capping, respray, repair, gutters, and pressure cleaning needs are captured in familiar homeowner language.<\\\\/p>/; s/<h3>Get a practical next step<\\\\/h3>/<h3>Receive a practical next step<\\\\/h3>/; s/Call now 0424 371 622 0424 371 622/Call now 0424 371 622/g' index.html\""}}

